[0.012, "o", "● k3s-agent.service - Lightweight Kubernetes\r\n     Loaded: loaded (\u001b]8;;file://supernova/etc/systemd/system/k3s-agent.service\u001b\\/etc/systemd/system/k3s-agent.service\u001b]8;;\u001b\\; \u001b[0;1;32menabled\u001b[0m; preset: \u001b[0;1;38:5:185mdisabled\u001b[0m)\r\n     Active: activating (start) since Thu 2026-07-02 17:01:15 WIB; 2min 51s ago\r\n        Job: 7342\r\n Invocation: 2ef63be510ed429f8fc53bb4d16999cd\r\n       Docs: \u001b]8;;https://k3s.io\u001b\\https://k3s.io\u001b]8;;\u001b\\\r\n    Process: 182201 ExecStartPre=/sbin/modprobe br_netfilter (code=exited, status=0/SUCCESS)\r\n    Process: 182203 ExecStartPre=/sbin/modprobe overlay (code=exited, status=0/SUCCESS)\r\n   Main PID: 182204 (k3s-agent)\r\n      Tasks: 13\r\n     Memory: 289.8M (peak: 380.2M)\r\n        CPU: 2.710s\r\n     CGroup: /system.slice/k3s-agent.service\r\n             └─\u001b[0;38:5:245m182204 \"/usr/local/bin/k3s agent\"\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nJul 02 17:03:47 supernova k3s[182204]: time=\"2026-07-02T17:03:47+07:00\" level=error msg=\"Failed to validate connection to cluster at https://10.244.56.235:6443: failed to get CA certs: Get \\\"https://127.0.0.1:6444/cacerts\\\": read tcp 127.0.0.1:37126->127.0.0.1:6444: read: connection reset by peer\"\r\nJul 02 17:03:49 supernova k3s[182204]: time=\"2026-07-02T17:03:49+07:00\" level=error msg=\"Failed to validate connection to cluster at https://10.244.56.235:6443: failed to get CA certs: Get \\\"https://127.0.0.1:6444/cacerts\\\": read tcp 127.0.0.1:37136->127.0.0.1:6444: read: connection reset by peer\"\r\nJul 02 17:03:51 supernova k3s[182204]: time=\"2026-07-02T17:03:51+07:00\" level=error msg=\"Failed to validate connection to cluster at https://10.244.56.235:6443: failed to get CA certs: Get \\\"https://127.0.0.1:6444/cacerts\\\": read tcp 127.0.0.1:33102->127.0.0.1:6444: read: connection reset by peer\"\r\nJul 02 17:03:53 supernova k3s[182204]: time=\"2026-07-02T17:03:53+07:00\" level=error msg=\"Failed to valida